{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">King of Beasts is a 3D third person survival and evolution game. In the perilous experimental field, players will control mutated creatures with special abilities, constantly fighting against other mutated creatures, evolving into more powerful creatures, surviving in terrifying alien experiments, and becoming the king of exotic beasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Evolutionary freedom, as long as you kill enemies, you can evolve into enemy form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perilous dangers lurk in the alien experimental field, and players need to remain vigilant at all times.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immersive experience, a grand and unique alien experimental field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/Shop1.png?t=1736300784\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Diverse characteristics, mutated organisms all possess unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fighting wits and courage, directly challenging powerful mutant creatures is not the best way. It requires the reasonable use of experimental field mechanisms and other mutant creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time limited survival, as time goes by, more and more powerful experimental subjects will join the battle and survive until the end to become the king of beasts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/extras/Shop2.png?t=1736300784\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736300784","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets